scuttle through the deep places of the world, creating massive
hive networks that stretch for miles.

arcane power, draining the region dry. Magic bounces
harmlessly from arcanamites as they swarm around they
targets, burrowing into them with razor-sharp pincers

dangerous, can provide a fortuitous haul. Spellcasters will

barbs to latch onto their target, draining arcane energy.
